title: J.J. Watt to the Cardinals and Moves That Could Change the Outlook of the 2021 Season
description:
Kevin and Nora start by discussing what J.J. Watt signing with the Arizona Cardinals does for their outlook next season (3:20). Then they talk about potential moves via free agency or trade that could completely change the outlook of a team (18:17).

Hosts: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
